This Device works with all sorts of Raspbery pis but this code is originally for the Raspberry Pi Zero 2w created.
Its functionating out of the boxwith this sorts of sensors: Max17048, DS18B20, Ebyte E220(LoRa), BMP 280
Einfach mit den Befehlen install.bash ausführen:
  chmod +x install.bash
  ./install.bash

































